              <div type="textpart" xml:id="Apparition4" xml:lang="gez">
                <label>The appearance of Jesus to His Apostles on the Sea of Tiberias; The miraculous draught of fishes; The appearance to Peter and to John</label>
                <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/PIRIKXW9"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:RompayArras1975Miracles"/><title level="a">Les manuscrits éthiopiens des ‘Miracles de Jésus’</title><title level="j">Analecta Bollandiana</title><author><forename>Lucas</forename><surname>Van Rompay</surname></author><author><forename>Victor</forename><surname>Arras</surname></author><date>1975</date><biblScope unit="volume">93</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">133-146</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:RompayArras1975Miracles</note></note><note type="tag">bm:RompayArras1975Miracles</note><citedRange unit="item">41</citedRange></bibl>
                <ab>
                  ዘከመ፡ ርእይዎ፡ አርድእት፡ እምድኅረ፡ ትንሣኤ፡ ውስተ፡ መቃብር።<gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወእምድኅረ፡ አስተርአዮሙ፡ ቅድመ፡ ስምዖን፡ ኬፋ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ ወዮሐንስ፡ ነጻርያነ፡ ምሥጢራት፡
                  ውስተ፡ ጽርሖሙ፡ ለያዕቆብ፡ ወለዮሐንስ፡ ወይቤሎሙ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ሑሩ፡ ወአሥግር፡ ዓሣ፡ በዛቲ፡ ሌሊት፡ ወይቤልዎ፡ ያዕቆብ፡ ወዮሐንስ፡ ወንሕነ፡ ንመጽእ፡ ምስሌከ፡ ወንትራድአከ።
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div type="textpart" xml:id="Apparition5" xml:lang="gez">
                <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/PIRIKXW9"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:RompayArras1975Miracles"/><title level="a">Les manuscrits éthiopiens des ‘Miracles de Jésus’</title><title level="j">Analecta Bollandiana</title><author><forename>Lucas</forename><surname>Van Rompay</surname></author><author><forename>Victor</forename><surname>Arras</surname></author><date>1975</date><biblScope unit="volume">93</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">133-146</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:RompayArras1975Miracles</note></note><note type="tag">bm:RompayArras1975Miracles</note><citedRange unit="item">42</citedRange></bibl>
                <label>Jesusʾ appearance in the cenacle; The Apostle Thomas sees and believes</label>
                <ab>
                  ወእምዝ፡ ተጋብኡ፡ አርድዕት፡ ውስተ፡ አሐቲ፡ ቤት፡ እንዘ፡ ይትኃብኡ፡ እምአይሁድ፡ የኃሥሡ፡ ይቅትልዎሙ፡ ወእንዘ፡ ይነብሩ፡ ውስተ፡ ጽርሐ፡ ኃዋኅዊሁ፡ ዕፅው፡ ላዕሌሆሙ፡ ርእዩ፡ ወናሁ፡ ብእሲ፡ ቦአ፡
                  ኀቤሆሙ፡ ወበዝኃ፡ አንክሮቶሙ፡ ወይቤሉ፡ በበይናቲሆሙ፡ እምአይቴ፡ ቦአ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ብእሲ፡ እንዘ፡ ዕፅው፡ ኃዋኅው።
                </ab>
              </div>
              <div type="textpart" xml:id="Apparition6">
                <label>The Ascension</label>
                <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/PIRIKXW9"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:RompayArras1975Miracles"/><title level="a">Les manuscrits éthiopiens des ‘Miracles de Jésus’</title><title level="j">Analecta Bollandiana</title><author><forename>Lucas</forename><surname>Van Rompay</surname></author><author><forename>Victor</forename><surname>Arras</surname></author><date>1975</date><biblScope unit="volume">93</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">133-146</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:RompayArras1975Miracles</note></note><note type="tag">bm:RompayArras1975Miracles</note><citedRange unit="item">43</citedRange></bibl>
                <ab>
                  በከመ፡ ዓርገ፡ ውስተ፡ ሰማያት።<gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወአመ፡ ፵ዕለት፡ እምድኅረ፡ ትንሣኤሁ፡ ለእግዚእነ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እምውስተ፡ መቃብር፡ አስተ<supplied reason="omitted">ር</supplied>አዮሙ፡ ለአርዳኢሁ፡ ወይቤሎሙ፡ ተጋብኡ፡
                  ኵልክሙ፡ ውስተ፡ ደብረ፡ ዘይት፡ ወተጋብኡ፡ ህየ፡ በከመ፡ ይቤሎሙ።

                </ab>
              </div>
          </div>
